<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

  {{> header title="Community - Rosetta"}}

  <body>

    <div class="site-wrapper">

      <!-- -->

      {{> page_header}}

      <!-- -->

      <section class="pt-160 pb-60">

        <div class="graphic-header">
          <img
            class="graphic-header__curve graphic-header__curve--brand-one"
            src="assets/svg/common/header-curve.svg"
            alt="Graphic of curve for aesthetics"
          />
          <object
            data="assets/svg/our-community/our-community.svg"
            type="image/svg+xml"
            class="graphic-header__graphic"
          ></object>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <p class="font-size-m7 mb-0">Trusted by the financial markets​</p>
              <h1 class="font-size-xl2 font-color-brand-one mb-45">Community</h1>
              <p>The new operating system for financial markets is open-source.
                <br />The industry is collaborating on Rosetta to build shared
                standards
                <br />for mission-critical business processes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- -->

      <section class="two-col-panel">
        <div class="body-curve">
          <canvas
            data-primary-color="#bddc5e"
            data-secondary-color="#e5f1bf"
            data-top-shape-svg-url="/assets/svg/curve/curve-e-top.svg"
            data-top-shape-y-offset-percentage="0"
            data-margin-top-percentage-of-top-shape-height="0"
            data-bottom-shape-svg-url="/assets/svg/curve/curve-d-bottom.svg"
            data-bottom-shape-y-offset-percentage="0"
            data-margin-bottom-percentage-of-bottom-shape-height="0"
          ></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="container body-curve-content pt-145 pb-65 pb-d-150">
          <div class="row">
            <div
              class="col-md-8 two-col-panel__col-details df-pb-t-50 display-flex flex-direction-column justify-content-center"
            >
              <h2 class="two-col-panel__heading" data-aos="fade-up"><span
                  class="font-color-brand-one"
                >Supported</span>
                <br />by the community</h2>
              <p>Accelerate your own projects by leveraging years of community
                investment into open-source, battle-tested industry models. Keep
                in sync with the latest model versions by design, no need to
                maintain that on your end.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 two-col-panel__col-graphic">
              <div
                class="horizontal-animation-graphic scrolls-into-view df-w-t-80p"
              >
                <div class="lottie-wrapper">
                  <lottie-player
                    autoplay
                    loop
                    mode="normal"
                    src="assets/lottie/built-for-the-community.json"
                    style="height: auto;"
                  ></lottie-player>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- -->

      <section
        class="two-col-panel background-color-brand-two"
        style="transform: translateY(-1px);"
      >
        <div class="body-curve">
          <canvas
            data-primary-color="#d7f0f3"
            data-secondary-color="#e7f6f8"
            data-top-shape-svg-url="/assets/svg/curve/curve-g-top.svg"
            data-top-shape-y-offset-percentage="0.1"
            data-margin-top-percentage-of-top-shape-height="0"
            data-bottom-shape-svg-url="/assets/svg/curve/curve-g-bottom.svg"
            data-bottom-shape-y-offset-percentage="0.1"
            data-margin-bottom-percentage-of-bottom-shape-height="0"
          ></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="container body-curve-content pt-225 pb-40 pb-d-150">
          <div class="row two-col-panel--reverse">
            <div
              class="col-md-8 two-col-panel__col-details df-pb-t-50 display-flex flex-direction-column justify-content-center"
            >
              <h2 class="two-col-panel__heading" data-aos="fade-up"><span
                  class="font-color-brand-one"
                >Collaborate on shared</span>
                <br />industry models</h2>
              <p>Some of the most complex industry processes are bi- or even
                multi-lateral. Rosetta enables native inter-operability between
                data users sitting across enterprise boundaries, by aligning their
                process implementation through shared code.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 two-col-panel__col-graphic">
              <div
                class="horizontal-animation-graphic horizontal-animation-graphic--mirror-anim scrolls-into-view df-w-t-80p"
              >
                <div class="lottie-wrapper">
                  <lottie-player
                    autoplay
                    loop
                    mode="normal"
                    src="assets/lottie/easy-and-fast-integration.json"
                    style="height: auto;"
                  ></lottie-player>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- -->

      <section class="pt-85 pb-25 background-color-brand-aux-six">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-5 pb-100 pb-ml-o-50">
              <p class="font-size-l1 font-weight-semi-bold">How industry
                associations use Rosetta</p>
              <p class="font-size-m2">Standardisation is the cornerstone of the
                digitisation of financial markets. Global trade associations and
                standard-setting organisations use Rosetta to build a "Common
                Domain Model" (CDM) and deliver a digital future for their
                market.​</p>

              <a
                href="{{ config.externalLinks.isda }}"
                class="link-with-graphic font-size-m5 font-weight-semi-bold mb-10"
                target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >
                Derivatives (ISDA)
                <i><img
                    src="assets/svg/common/link-with-arrow.svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                  /></i>
              </a>
              <a
                href="{{ config.externalLinks.isla }}"
                class="link-with-graphic font-size-m5 font-weight-semi-bold mb-10"
                target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >
                Securities Financing (ISLA)
                <i><img
                    src="assets/svg/common/link-with-arrow.svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                  /></i>
              </a>
              <a
                href="{{ config.externalLinks.icma }}"
                class="link-with-graphic font-size-m5 font-weight-semi-bold"
                target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >
                Bond and Repo (ICMA)
                <i><img
                    src="assets/svg/common/link-with-arrow.svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                  /></i>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 offset-md-2 pb-100 pb-ml-o-50">
              <p class="font-size-l1 font-weight-semi-bold">How technology
                providers use Rosetta</p>
              <p class="font-size-m2">New technology, from cloud to distributed
                ledger to machine learning, are re-defining how financial markets
                operate. Technology providers, large and small, leverage Rosetta's
                executable code distribution to accelerate their time-to-market.</p>
              <a
                href="{{ config.externalLinks.ethereum }}"
                class="link-with-graphic font-size-m5 font-weight-semi-bold mb-10"
                target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >
                Axoni (Ethereum)
                <i><img
                    src="assets/svg/common/link-with-arrow.svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                  /></i>
              </a>
              <a
                href="{{ config.externalLinks.corda }}"
                class="link-with-graphic font-size-m5 font-weight-semi-bold mb-10"
                target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >
                Fragmos (Corda)
                <i><img
                    src="assets/svg/common/link-with-arrow.svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                  /></i>
              </a>
              <a
                href="{{ config.externalLinks.isdaCreate }}"
                class="link-with-graphic font-size-m5 font-weight-semi-bold"
                target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >
                ISDA Create
                <i><img
                    src="assets/svg/common/link-with-arrow.svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                  /></i>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 pb-100 pb-ml-o-50">
              <p class="font-size-l1 font-weight-semi-bold">How financial
                institutions use Rosetta</p>
              <p class="font-size-m2">Whether for clearing, trade lifecycle
                management, collateral management or reporting, Rosetta helps
                financial institutions re-engineer their post-trade business
                processes.</p>
              <a
                href="{{ config.externalLinks.postTrade }}"
                class="link-with-graphic font-size-m5 font-weight-semi-bold mb-10"
                target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >
                Post-trade processing
                <i><img
                    src="assets/svg/common/link-with-arrow.svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                  /></i>
              </a>
              <a
                href="{{ config.externalLinks.regulatoryReporting }}"
                class="link-with-graphic font-size-m5 font-weight-semi-bold"
                target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >
                Regulatory reporting
                <i><img
                    src="assets/svg/common/link-with-arrow.svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                  /></i>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5 offset-md-2 pb-100 pb-ml-o-50">
              <p class="font-size-l1 font-weight-semi-bold">How regulators use
                Rosetta</p>
              <p class="font-size-m2">Rosetta is at the forefront of the
                digitisation of the financial regulatory framework, helping
                regulators around the globe transform their data collection
                process through "machine-executable regulation" or
                "rules-as-code".</p>
              <a
                href="{{ config.externalLinks.machineExecutable }}"
                class="link-with-graphic font-size-m5 font-weight-semi-bold mb-10"
                target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >
                Machine-executable regulation
                <i><img
                    src="assets/svg/common/link-with-arrow.svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                  /></i>
              </a>
              <a
                href="{{ config.externalLinks.dataModelling }}"
                class="link-with-graphic font-size-m5 font-weight-semi-bold"
                target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              >
                Data Modelling
                <i><img
                    src="assets/svg/common/link-with-arrow.svg"
                    loading="lazy"
                  /></i>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- -->

      <section
        class="pt-110 pb-10 text-align-center position-relative background-color-brand-aux-six"
      >
        <div class="body-curve">
          <canvas
            data-primary-color="#ea409d"
            data-secondary-color="#ee89c1"
            data-top-shape-svg-url="/assets/svg/curve/curve-e-top.svg"
            data-top-shape-y-offset-percentage="0"
            data-margin-top-percentage-of-top-shape-height="0"
            data-bottom-shape-svg-url="/assets/svg/curve/curve-e-bottom-alt-1.svg"
            data-bottom-shape-y-offset-percentage="0.1"
            data-margin-bottom-percentage-of-bottom-shape-height="0"
          ></canvas>
        </div>
        <div class="container body-curve-content">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <p
                class="font-weight-semi-bold mb-20 font-color-brand-two"
                data-aos="fade-up"
              >Ready to roll?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row mb-60">
            <div class="col-md-12 mb-25">
              <h2
                class="font-color-brand-aux-two font-size-l6r"
                data-aos="fade-up"
              >Take Rosetta for a spin.
                <br class="display-none d-b-m-o" /><span
                  class="font-color-brand-two"
                >It's on us.</span>​
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12 mb-25">
              <div class="button-card mb-20" data-aos="fade-up">
                <a
                  href="{{ config.externalLinks.signUp }}"
                  class="button"
                >Sign up for free</a>
              </div>
              <div class="button-card mb-20" data-aos="fade-up">
                <a href="pricing" class="button">Buy now</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <p
                class="font-size-m2 font-color-brand-aux-two"
                data-aos="fade-up"
              >Sign-up today and get started on your model development in seconds.
                <br class="d-n-m-o d-n-ml-o" />Our free version comes with no time
                limit and no credit card required.
                <br class="d-n-m-o d-n-i-o" />And Rosetta can then grow with your
                enterprise use. ​​​</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- -->

      {{> footer}}

      <!-- -->

      <div class="mini-header-trigger"></div>

    </div>

    <!-- -->

